text: Solenosmilia is a genus of small corals in the family Caryophylliidae. ==Species== The World Register of Marine Species includes the following species in the genus : *Solenosmilia australis Cairns & Polonio, 2013 *Solenosmilia variabilis Duncan, 1873 ==References== Category:Caryophylliidae Category:Scleractinia genera
title: Solenosmilia
